Revision history for XML::XSP

0.4.2 (10-04-2004)
  - Fixed XML::XSP::Driver::LibXSLT to handle dealing with document
    fragments
  - Updated LibXSLT driver to work with XML::LibXML 1.56/XML::LibXSLT 1.53
  - Fixed md5_hex warning with URI references 
  - Fixed xsp:attribute & xsp:element tags when nested in xsp:logic & xsp:expr tags
  - Added extra test cases
  - Updated copyright notice
  - Fixed xsp:page language bug
  - Added real xsp:page & fixed append to document root bug

0.4.1 (13-05-2002)
  - Fixed XML::XSP::Driver::LibXSLT file handler bug
  - Tweaked logging output
  - Fixed internal state inconsistences when an exception is thrown
    with a page
  - Fixed exception handling in test scripts
  - Disabled memory test by default
  - Updated LibXSLT driver to work with XML::LibXML 1.49

0.4.0 (25-02-2002)
  - Fix logging to deal with exceptions objects
  - Added documentation
  - Fixed XML::XSP::Driver::LibXSLT to better survive forking

0.3.1 (23-02-2002)
  - We now keep cache internal all pages compiled against a URI
  - Added first pass at page unloader
  - Added xsp:comment, xsp:pi, xsp:content

0.3.0 (23-02-2002)
  - Added XML::XSP::Log to handle logging
  - Added option to set callback for the log handler
  - Added Taglib option to Page, to disable application of Taglibs
    stylesheet
  - Added XML::XSP::Exception
  - Cleaned up internal API
  - Added improved test harness

0.2.1 (07-02-2002)
  - Moved over to using XML::LibXML & XML::LibXSLT 1.30
  - Fixed recusive calling of cached xsp:logic page segmentation fault
  - xsp:page now apply-templates to attributes

0.2.0 (19-11-2001)
  - Fixed bug with <xsp:expr></xsp:expr>
  - Fixed bug for deep nested <xsp:logic> & <xsp:expr>
  - Added example test checking
  - Added memory leak testing
  - Fixed taglib support in CORE
  - Added as-string & as-expr helper templates
  - Cleaned up MANIFEST

0.0.5 (25-10-2001)
  - Added xsp:text support
  - Added xsp:logic support
  - Added namespacing option for xsp::attribute & xsp:element
  - Fixed recursive xsp tag behaviour

0.0.1 
  - Original version